<h3><strong>Specific Usage Tips </strong></h3>
<h4><strong>How to use Playfair Display for logos?</strong></h4>
<p>Editorial or fashion brands. For example, Online magazines, fashion-focused communities, or marketplaces.</p>
<h4><strong>How to use Playfair Display for marketing and branding?</strong></h4>
<p>Playfair Display is a display font. Use for showy purposes only, like social media. The thinnest parts of high contrast fonts will break down at small scales. Don’t use this font for small texts, like paragraphs.</p>
